- Individual rats are irrelevant—treat entire swarm as single creature
- Guard: 10-15, Vitality: 40-60 (depending on swarm size)
- Damage: 1d6 to everyone in the zone
- Special: Area effects do double damage, swarm splits if reduced to half vitality

